> 2001 economic crisis in Turkey.
> January 5 - Burak Gunduz was born.
> 1 March - World Bank vice president Kemal Dervis came to Turkey upon the invitation of Bulent Ecevit.
> April 25 - Murat Tokez was born.
> May 16 - CASA type military cargo plane manufactured by TAI crashed near Akcadag district of Malatya. 34 soldiers, 10 of whom were Turks, died.
> March 22 - Sabiha Gokcen (the first female fighter pilot) dies.
> July 9 - Yusuf Furkan Demiryurek was born.